    "“Online” means this account's runtime worker is active in the app right now (subscribed to its relays). It doesn't reflect key access." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the meaning of \"online\" in the context of an account's status.",
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "„Online“ bedeutet, dass der Laufzeit-Worker dieses Kontos gerade in der App aktiv ist (seine Relays abonniert hat). Es spiegelt nicht den Schlüsselzugriff wider."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"En línea\" significa que el trabajador en tiempo de ejecución de esta cuenta está activo en la aplicación en este momento (suscrito a sus retransmisiones). No refleja el acceso clave."
          }
        },
        "fr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "« En ligne » signifie que le travailleur d'exécution de ce compte est actuellement actif dans l'application (abonné à ses relais). Cela ne reflète pas l'accès par clé."
          }
        },
        "it" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Online\" significa che il lavoratore runtime di questo account è attivo nell'app in questo momento (iscritto ai suoi relè). Non riflette l'accesso alla chiave."
          }
        },
        "pt" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“Online” significa que o trabalhador de tempo de execução desta conta está ativo no aplicativo no momento (inscrito em seus relés). Não reflete o acesso à chave."
          }
        },
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "«В сети» означает, что рабочий процесс выполнения этой учетной записи активен в приложении прямо сейчас (подписан на его ретрансляторы). Это не отражает ключевой доступ."
          }
        },
        "tr" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "\"Çevrimiçi\", bu hesabın çalışma zamanı çalışanının şu anda uygulamada etkin olduğu (aktarmalarına abone olduğu) anlamına gelir. Anahtar erişimini yansıtmaz."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "“Online” means this account's runtime worker is active in the app right now (subscribed to its relays).它不反映密钥访问。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "「線上」表示該帳戶的執行時間工作人員現在在應用程式中處於活動狀態（訂閱了其中繼）。它不反映密鑰存取。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
